  "texts": [
    "In addition, a Random Forest is easier to train and tune.",
    "A bootstraping method was used as cross validation to optimize the model complexity.",
    "In addition to the Random Forest method, we tested the classification using Adaboost, Extra Trees, and Logistic Regression methods.",
    "Methods obtained very similar results, however, Random Forest outperformed the other three using the same train and test sets.",
    "Results are summarised in Table 2."
  ]
